Package: crisprapex
Title: Find crispr set to target a set of loci for CRISPR-APEX experiments
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Aditya", "Bhagwat", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = c("aditya.bhagwat@mpi-bn.mpg.de", "bhagwataditya@gmail.com"))
Description: Contains functions to find a crispr set to target a set of genomic 
 loci for CRISPR-APEX experiments. Targeting flanks of genomic loci rather than 
 loci themselves is made easy. Functions have been made efficient, benefiting 
 from data.table and Biostrings.
